data.description: Seller to entertain offers between $999,000-$1,049,000.  Cozy living with pride of ownership inside and out! Welcome home! This 4 bed, 2.5 bath home is located in the prestigious neighborhood of Eastlake Trails. Exterior features and upgrades include new exterior paint, drought resistant landscape in the front of the home with paver driveway and hardscape, Large backyard with mature landscaping, artificial turf, Alumawood pergola, and paver hardscape. Interior features and upgrades include large kitchen with custom island, corian countertops, laminate floors and an extra large primary bedroom. Walk to the Olympic Training Center, local parks, schools, pools, and shopping.
